-- Tharisa Minerals Secures $133 Million In Funding From HSBC for Chrome Mine
-- B y   J a n a   M a r a i s
-- 2012-03-05T05:25:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-05/tharisa-minerals-secures-133-million-in-funding-from-hsbc-for-chrome-mine.html
Tharisa Minerals (Pty) Ltd. secured
1 billion rand in finance from  HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA)  for a 4.8
million metric ton chrome and platinum mine and concentrator
plant in  South Africa .  HSBC made the announcement in an advertisement in
Johannesburg-based Business Day today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Marais in Johannesburg at 
 jmarais@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  